msgstr "ຂະໜາດແພັກເກັດການປິງ"

#: applications/luci-app-watchcat/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/watchcat.js:27
msgid "Ping Reboot"
msgstr "ຣີບູດດ້ວຍການປິງ"

#: applications/luci-app-watchcat/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/watchcat.js:23
msgid ""
"Ping Reboot: Reboot this device if a ping to a specified host fails for a "
"specified duration of time. <br /> Periodic Reboot: Reboot this device after "
"a specified interval of time. <br /> Restart Interface: Restart a network "
"interface if a ping to a specified host fails for a specified duration of "
"time. <br /> Run Script: Run a script if a ping to a specified host fails "
"for a specified duration of time. <br />"
msgstr ""
"ຣີບູດດ້ວຍການປິງ: ຣີບູດອຸປະກອນນີ້ ຫາກການປິງຫາໂຮສຕ໌ທີ່ລະບຸໄວ້ລົ້ມເຫຼວຕາມໄລຍະເວລາທີ່ກຳນົດ. <br /> ຣີບູດ"
"ຕາມກຳນົດເວລາ: ຣີບູດອຸປະກອນນີ້ ຫຼັງຈາກຄົບກຳນົດເວລາທີ່ລະບຸໄວ້. <br /> ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນອິນເຕີເຟດໃໝ່: ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນອິນ"
"ເຕີເຟດເຄືອຂ່າຍໃໝ່ ຫາກການປິງຫາໂຮສຕ໌ທີ່ລະບຸໄວ້ລົ້ມເຫຼວຕາມໄລຍະເວລາທີ່ກຳນົດ. <br /> ລັນສະຄຣິບ: ຣັນສະ"
"ຄຣິບ ຫາກການປິງຫາໂຮສຕ໌ທີ່ລະບຸໄວ້ລົ້ມເຫຼວຕາມໄລຍະເວລາທີ່ກຳນົດ. <br />"

#: applications/luci-app-watchcat/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/watchcat.js:29
msgid "Restart Interface"
msgstr "ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນອິນເຕີເຟດໃໝ່"

#: applications/luci-app-watchcat/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/watchcat.js:30
msgid "Run Script"
msgstr "ລັນສະຄຣິບ"

#: applications/luci-app-watchcat/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/watchcat.js:33
msgid "Script to run"
msgstr "ສະຄຣິບທີ່ຈະຣັນ"

#: applications/luci-app-watchcat/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/watchcat.js:34
msgid ""
"Script to run when the host has not responded for the specified duration of "
"time. The script is passed the interface name as $1"
msgstr ""
"ສະຄຣິບທີ່ຈະຣັນ ເມື່ອໂຮສຕ໌ບໍ່ມີການຕອບສະໜອງຕາມໄລຍະເວລາທີ່ກຳນົດ. ສະຄຣິບຈະຖືກສົ່ງຄ່າຊື່ອິນເຕີເຟດເປັນ $1"

#: applications/luci-app-watchcat/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/watchcat.js:81
msgid "Small: 1 byte"
msgstr "ນ້ອຍ: 1 ໄບຕ໌"

#: applications/luci-app-watchcat/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/watchcat.js:83
msgid "Standard: 56 bytes"
msgstr "ມາດຕະຖານ: 56 ໄບຕ໌"

#: applications/luci-app-watchcat/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/watchcat.js:15
msgid "These rules will govern how this device reacts to network events."
msgstr "ກົດເຫຼົ່ານີ້ຈະກຳນົດວິທີທີ່ອຸປະກອນນີ້ຕອບສະໜອງຕໍ່ເຫດການເຄືອຂ່າຍ."

#: applications/luci-app-watchcat/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/watchcat.js:117
